SELECT sekolah_id as instansi_id,'' as kode_instansi, s.nama as nama_sekolah, s.nama as nama, npsn, s.kode_wilayah as kode_wilayah, status_sekolah, r1.nama as provinsi, r2.nama as kota, r3.nama as kecamatan FROM [arsip].[dbo].[sekolah] s LEFT JOIN Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah r1 on LEFT(r1.kode_wilayah, 2) = LEFT (s.kode_wilayah, 2) AND r1.id_level_wilayah=1 LEFT JOIN Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah r2 on LEFT(r2.kode_wilayah, 4) = LEFT (s.kode_wilayah, 4) AND r2.id_level_wilayah=2 LEFT JOIN Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah r3 on LEFT(r3.kode_wilayah, 6) = LEFT (s.kode_wilayah, 6) AND r3.id_level_wilayah=3 WHERE npsn = '20104472'
